To make Yammer an important and regular part of your day, try a few of these practical suggestions:

- Update your profile with information others might want to know about you\.
- Follow different people, topics, or a conversation\.
- Join a few groups, like a topic, team, or project that interests you\. Don’t forget to “Like” what you see\.
- Once a week, praise a coworker who has gone above and beyond\.
- When you have a question, use Yammer search to get the answer\.
- Try the Discovery feed to learn relevant information across the Yammer network\.
- Spend a few minutes each day in your Inbox to stay up\-to\-date\.

__Edit a document__

1. Click on the file you wish to edit from the __Files__list, or click __Go to file__ on a document in your feed\.
2. On the right side of the screen, click __Edit file__\. 
3. Make your edits in Word Online, PowerPoint Online, or Excel Online\.
